0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32714,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/cures-physical-mental-spiritual\/","url_meta":{"origin":32737,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Healing: Cures for every physical, mental, spiritual disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent down the cure.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5354 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Qayyim said, \u201cThis is generally true for diseases of the heart, the spirit, the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31845,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/hasan-hawa-spiritual-disease\/","url_meta":{"origin":32737,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Whims: Lowly desires worst spiritual disease of hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhims are the worst disease to interfere with a heart.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 14131 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0621 \u0634\u064e\u0631\u0651\u064f \u062f\u064e\u06